<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>0</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>6255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong stood before Guanyin.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He was telling the bodhisattva everything [n@that had happened at the monastery.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Then a bear spirit called the Black Wind King [n@stole the robe," the monkey went on.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I demanded he give it back.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>We fought—until the bear spirit said it was lunchtime and hid in his cave.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>I kicked the door and yelled insults at him for more than an hour.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@But he wouldn't come out.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>You must help me."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Guanyin sighed. "The Tang Monk should not have [n@shown that robe to the priest," she said.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"The robe is a Buddhist treasure.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>When other people see it, they will want it.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>And as that head priest tried to do, they might harm the Tang Monk."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I agree," said Wukong.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I've told the Tang Monk many times not to do dumb things. But still he—"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"And you should have put out that fire," Guanyin said, interrupting Wukong.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"What you did was terrible!"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong looked at the ground.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@He kicked a pebble.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I know," he mumbled.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I'll help you get back the robe," said Guanyin. "Let's go."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong and Guanyin soared over the ocean.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Soon they landed on the mountain.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Where is the Black Wind King's cave?" asked Guanyin.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"It's close," said Wukong.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"We should sneak up to it."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>They heard footsteps coming closer.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong and Guanyin hid as a Daoist priest walked along the path.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@The priest was holding a tray.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A bright purple pill sat on the tray.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@The priest was talking to himself.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"This is an exciting day," he said.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"The Black Wind King has a new robe that is a Buddhist treasure.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>And I hope he likes the pill I made for him.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>It will make him live forever."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Wukong stared at the priest, using his magic sight.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"That's not a priest!" Wukong realized.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"It's a wolf spirit dressed as a priest."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The monkey's eyes lit up.@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I have an idea, Bodhisattva!"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A little while later, the priest stood before [n@the Black Wind King's cave door.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He knocked and the door flew open.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Are you still here, you little monkey?" shouted the Black Wind King.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Then he saw the priest and smiled.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Oh, it's you, my old friend!@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@Sorry for yelling.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A pesky monkey spirit was here a little while ago."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@He looked around.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I guess he's gone."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"A monkey spirit was here?" asked the priest.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Yes," said the bear.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"He kept banging on my door and yelling at me.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He was very rude."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The Black Wind King patted the priest on the shoulder.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"But let's not talk about him.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@It's good to see you.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>How have you been?"@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I'm well," said the priest.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"I brought you a gift, to celebrate your new Buddhist treasure."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>He held up the tray with the pill.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@The Black Wind King looked interested.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"What kind of pill is that?"@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"It is a very special pill," said the priest with a smile.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[g@"I made it just for you.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>It will make you live forever."@g]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The Black Wind King stroked his chin.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"You know, I was just thinking this morning [n@that I would like to live forever."</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>The bear picked up the pill and opened his mouth wide.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>As he brought the pill up to his mouth, the pill wiggled.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"Huh? Did the pill just—"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>But before the Black Wind King could finish [n@speaking, the pill hopped off his hand.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>It shot into his mouth and slid down his throat.</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>[i@Gulp!@i]</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>